{"tid":1424851,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"連登就真係自由民主既倒模","createTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:12.000Z","updateTime":"2019-08-06T17:19:05.000Z","uid":81236,"like":77,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"7fd11c42cf479b3887c8edb67bf8f5e241d6f71c","tid":1424851,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:12.000Z","msg":"連登既管治根本就係一直想追求屬於真係香港人政府管治方案<br />\n<br />\n1) 聆聽民意<br />\n因為聽到唔少會員反映近期黑色五毛警示，加入隱藏顯示正負評避免比五毛帶風分化<br />\n<br />\n2) 因時制宜<br />\n因應香港緊急情況多人上連登，主動取消廣告以增加瀏覽速度<br />\n<br />\n3) 以民為本<br />\n多項措施同功能都係以用家體驗為主<br />\n<br />\n4) 管治透明<br />\n因應有懷疑post被帶風而作出調查，並清晰公佈調查結果<br />\n<br />\n5) 不畏強權保障個人私隱<br />\n主動取消顯示註冊電郵，相信有唔少&rdquo;機構&rdquo;要求連登出賣個人資料<br />\n<br />\n多謝連住尼同埋一眾管理團隊對追求自由民主既堅持，勇敢面對強權。希望連登既管理層可以守住防線，等大家可以係到自由發表發夢言論。<br />\n<br />\n我謹以連登為是次光復香港運動大本營，以追求屬於香港人既民主自由。<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/drum.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/whip.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/bye.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/shocked.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/knife.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/bark.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/escape.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/itdog3.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/math.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"373dc19bcd04c9ffe6751b451690ea781189b75b","tid":1424851,"uid":154796,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:40:46.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/lihkg.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"72dd375d27dd665943a8279b8eea6bc17cb21b99","tid":1424851,"uid":172914,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:42:50.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/dance2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2a9dbb2f2c664ad4c71bcb05655f97d9e35a57e3","tid":1424851,"uid":102609,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:42:51.000Z","msg":"連仔要加油頂住班邪惡勢力<br />\n香港最自由嘅網上平台靠你守住喇<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/notcry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"aa59a3de5d1166beb57957f64b596b4fa3dc2995","tid":1424851,"uid":4180,"like":5,"dislike":1,"score":4,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:44:05.000Z","msg":"連登=我心目中運動既mvp <img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n不過連登係愛國撐警<br />\nBabykingdom同香討先係黃絲集中營<img src=\"/assets/faces/big/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6096af83b6b8acb95240feaa807d90507e9934b7","tid":1424851,"uid":81236,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:45:36.000Z","msg":"比你寧願交稅定課金<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/upset.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"7cb584142bd8f35c8bc3a295a32784af7b86fd8e","tid":1424851,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"起碼有行動同埋都幾實際先"},{"pid":"d3d5f26e9f1ae22e71ff89f93f1a55a4aaf3b5f7","tid":1424851,"uid":81236,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"7cb584142bd8f35c8bc3a295a32784af7b86fd8e","tid":1424851,"uid":34023,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:46:40.000Z","msg":"起碼有行動同埋都幾實際先"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:50:20.000Z","msg":"因應情況主動取消廣告已經係無得輸"},{"pid":"1916c855b9f45bce2940e15b75ab9cd9840945ce","tid":1424851,"uid":32022,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-08-06T16:53:38.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/dog/fight_connect.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"}